dcterms:description: The CIFAR10 dataset contains 50,000 training images and 10,000 test images, belonging to 10 classes. The training images were randomly split into a training set of 40,000 images and a validation set of 10,000 images.
dcterms:title: CIFAR10

dcterms:creator: A. Krizhevsky
G. Hinton
dcterms:description: The CIFAR100 dataset also contains 50,000 training images and 10,000 test images, belonging to 100 classes. The training images were randomly split into a training set of 40,000 images and a validation set of 10,000 images.
dcterms:title: CIFAR100

dcterms:creator: J. Wu
Q. Zhang
G. Xu
dcterms:description: The Tiny ImageNet dataset contains 100,000 training images and 10,000 test images, belonging to 200 classes. The training images were randomly split into a training set of 90,000 images and a validation set of 10,000 images.
dcterms:title: Tiny ImageNet
